{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":22450,"duration_api_ms":20963,"ttft_ms":9682,"num_turns":2,"result":"CLI が `blocking_reasons: [\"failed_required_artifact\"]` を返したため、ここで停止します。\n\n---\n\n## 停止通知: `failed_required_artifact`\n\nCLIの指示: **`run /spec-core or /spec-core --all before /spec-realign`**\n\n### 失敗した必須アーティファクト\n\n| アーティファクト | 状態 | 詳細 |\n|---|---|---|\n| `retrieval_index` | failed | Source Retrieval Index の更新に失敗 |\n| `related_sections` | failed | Qdrant バックエンドへの接続拒否 (`http://localhost:65530`) |\n\n### 警告内容\n\n- `Source Retrieval Index update failed`\n- `Related Sections retrieval backend failure: [Errno 111] Connection refused; canonical related_sections artifact is not updated. Restore Qdrant connectivity and run /spec-core --rebuild.`\n\n### 復旧手順\n\n1. **Qdrant の起動確認** — `localhost:65530` で Qdrant が起動しているか確認してください\n2. **アーティファクト再生成** — 以下のいずれかを実行してください:\n   ```\n   /spec-core\n   ```\n   または全再生成の場合:\n   ```\n   /spec-core --all\n   ```\n3. Qdrant の接続が回復できない場合は `/spec-core --rebuild` を実行してください\n4. 上記完了後、改めて `/spec-realign` を実行してください\n\n回答の整形は、必須アーティファクトが揃うまで実行できません。","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"1856fb08-d580-459c-a1e4-ea142fcebffd","total_cost_usd":0.08033280000000001,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":14164,"cache_read_input_tokens":38786,"output_tokens":1038,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":14164,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":432,"cache_read_input_tokens":25316,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2318,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2318},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":4,"outputTokens":1038,"cacheReadInputTokens":38786,"cacheCreationInputTokens":14164,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.08033280000000001,"co